name: AMEAddMultitrackDocumentToQueueEvent

properties.name: EVENT_ADDMULTITRACKDOCUMENTTOQUEUE_ERROR
properties.description: An event with this type is propagated if a multitrack document failed to be added to the Adobe Media Encoder queue
properties.longdesc: Add to queue failed event type

properties.name: EVENT_ADDMULTITRACKDOCUMENTTOQUEUE_SUCCESS
properties.description: An event with this type is propagated if a multitrack document was added to the Adobe Media Encoder queue successfully
properties.longdesc: Add to queue succeeded event type

properties.name: message
properties.description: Provides additional information for this event esspecially in the case of an error.

description: An event to inform about succes or failures of an add multitrack document to queue operation.
